OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with some lengthy sunshine
OL,6,Fto start but soon clouding over for
OL,7,Fthe Western Isles and west coast.
OL,8,FCloud spreading southeast to all
OL,9,Fthrough the afternoon with patchy
OL,10,Flight rain. Warm in the east in any
OL,11,Fsunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will stay cloudy through
OL,14,Fthe evening and overnight. Some light
OL,15,Frain or drizzle affecting much of the
OL,16,Fregion but staying dry towards
OL,17,FInverness and Nairn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
