OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA cloudy start for all with
OL,6,Fpatchy rain or drizzle in the west.
OL,7,FEastern parts brightening up through
OL,8,Fthe afternoon with some warm sunshine.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,11,FStaying largely cloudy with spells of
OL,12,Flight rain in the west. Staying
OL,13,Flargely dry with a few bright spells
OL,14,Ftowards Inverness and Nairn.
OL,15,FFreshening westerly winds on Thursday
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
